    <item>
      <title>《信贷周刊》：押注高风险 CLO 可带来 20% 的收益</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-25/bets-on-risky-clos-are-paying-off-with-20-gains-credit-weekly</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着贷款业绩改善、债务利差收窄和支出增长，抵押贷款债券中风险最高的部分的回报率正在大幅上升，大西洋两岸的回报率年化率均达到 20% 左右。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-25/bets-on-risky-clos-are-paying-off-with-20-gains-credit-weekly</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 25 May 2024 19:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>BP南非公司与壳牌下游炼油厂资产出售</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-25/bp-southern-africa-shell-downstream-to-sell-refinery-assets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[BP 南非（私人）有限公司和壳牌南非下游（私人）有限公司已达成协议，将其各自持有的南非最大炼油厂资产的 50% 股份出售给国有中央能源基金 SOC 有限公司。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-25/bp-southern-africa-shell-downstream-to-sell-refinery-assets</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 25 May 2024 16:53:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>上田暗示日本收益率处于 12 年高点并不是主要问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-25/ueda-hints-japan-yields-at-12-year-high-aren-t-a-major-issue</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本央行行长上田一夫表示，他对长期债券收益率升至2012年以来最高水平没有太大问题，并称长期债券收益率应由市场引导。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-25/ueda-hints-japan-yields-at-12-year-high-aren-t-a-major-issue</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 25 May 2024 15:04:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
